                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/fd/aktuelt/nyheter/2010/Viktig-samarbeidsavtale-mellom-Norge-og-Polen.html?id=613940" title="">
                        Important cooperation agreement between Norway and Poland
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[News story, Ministry of Defence, 10.09.2010]</p>
                <p>On 7 September 2010 the Norwegian Ministry of Defence entered into an agreement with the Polish Ministry of Defence concerning increased cooperation on defence equipment.</p>
                
                
