                <p class="ArticleInfo">[News story, Ministry of Defence, 10.09.2010]</p>
                <p>“This is a big and important day for Norway as a coastal nation. We have much to defend, and with HNoMS Storm and the Skjold Class we are better equipped than ever before,” says State Secretary Roger Ingebrigtsen who was attending the naming ceremony of HNoMS Storm.</p>
                
                
