                        Message to the 2010 World Conference against Atomic and Hydrogen Bombs
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Speech/article, Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 06.08.2010]</p>
                <p>"A world free of nuclear weapons is a longstanding aim of Norway’s foreign policy, and was so even during the Cold War", Foreign Minister Jonas Gahr Støre writes in his message to the World Conference Against Atomic and Hydrogen Bombs, Hiroshima, 6 august 2010.</p>
                
                
