                        International Conference on Afghanistan
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none">Kabul, 20 July 2010</h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Speech/article, Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 20.07.2010]</p>
                <p>"We – who contribute to Afghanistan’s future with both troops and funds - have the right to expect from President Karzai and his government, that you follow up with dedication on the plans that you have developed and that we have supported", Foreign Minister Støre said in his speech in Kabul 20 July 2010.</p>
                
                
